    "node_id": "IC_kwDOAJy4As5x-og_",
    "body": "Reading my reply, maybe `// Adapted from: ...` might be better since you may have to change the function signature like the receiver or maybe change some of the internals to refer to structs properly, of course.  In other words, you may have to edit it, but I would think \"Adapted from\" might be more appriopriate than \"Copied from\", but your call... I think either is probably fine as long as you have the copyright message in there.",
